Calool-dhalaalka ayaa sidoo kale laga arkaa bukaannada qaarkood.
Cudurka sanbabadu waa mid ka mid ah calaamadaha ugu daran wuxuuna si dhakhso leh ugu sii socon karaa cudurka neefsashada oo degdeg ah.
In kasta oo SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV-2 ay aad isugu egyihiin sababtoo ah isku midka taxanaha nuucliotide ee sareeya ee 82%, waxay isku urursadaan laamo kala duwan oo ku jira geedka phylogenetic.
