10 Abriil 2020, Google iyo Apple waxay si wada jir ah u shaaciyeen inay ku dari doonaan shaqeyn u taageera barnaamijyada Bluetooth-ka ku saleysan si toos ah nidaamyadooda hawlgalka ee Android iyo iOS.
