Labada Australia iyo New Zealand labaduba waxay ka fiirsanayaan barnaamijyo ku saleysan barnaamijka TraceTogether ee Singapore iyo borotokoolka BlueTrace. Ruushka wuxuu damacsan yahay inuu soo bandhigo barnaamij geofencing ah bukaannada laga helay COVID-19 ee ku nool Moscow, oo loogu talagalay in lagu hubiyo inaysan guriga ka bixin.
Ross Anderson, oo ah borofisar ka dhiga injineernimada amniga jaamacada Cambridge, ayaa liis gareeyay dhibaatooyin badan oo suurtagal ah oo ku saabsan nidaamyada ku saleysan barnaamijyada, oo ay ku jiraan natiijooyinka been abuurka ah iyo suurtagalnimada waxtar la'aanta haddii isticmaalka barnaamijka uu ku koobnaado kaliya qayb yar oo ka mid ah dadka.
Si wax looga qabto walaaca ku saabsan faafitaanka barnaamijyada "coronavirus" ee khaldamaya ama waxyeelada leh, Apple waxay xaddiday noocyada ururada ay ku dari karaan barnaamijyada la xiriira coronavirus-ka App Store-keeda, iyaga oo ku xaddidaya oo keliya "rasmi" ama ururro kale oo sumcad leh.
