Tijaabooyinka wajiga I-II waxay sameeyaan baaritaano horudhac ah oo ku saabsan badbaadada iyo immunogenicity, sida caadiga ah waa randomized, placebo-controlled, iyo goobo badan, halka la go'aaminayo qiyaaso sax ah oo waxtar leh.
